  "texts": [
    "Using this pattern would help the project to create initial requirements and furthermore generally in requirements management.",
    "Requirements Creation Pattern Contextual statements: \"As a [roleA] your task is to create a requirement specification.",
    "The requirement specification must fulfil the following constraints: [c1, c2, c3…].Ask the necessary questions to fully understand the constraints.",
    "Based on my answers create the requirement specification.",
    "Explain your understanding and construct your proposal to me representing the [roleB]."
